Bring that audience with you to social media and give

00:11:28.621 --> 00:11:32.361
people an inner look into your supposed private life.

00:11:33.431 --> 00:11:36.681
Use the social media algorithms to grow your audience.

00:11:37.421 --> 00:11:42.061
Continually talk about your life, your beauty routine and the products that

00:11:42.061 --> 00:11:46.941
you use, and give your hundreds of millions of social media followers the

00:11:46.951 --> 00:11:51.521
